  <brief_title>Tissue Study of Bv8/PK-2 Inhibition in Human Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Human Primary Cancer Tissue Implanted in Mice Lacking Bv8/PH-2 in Their Bone Marrow-derived Cells</official_title>
  <sponsors>
